sections.heading: taxes; lien on real estate; priority
sections.text: The first lien upon real estate under section 77-203 shall take priority over all other encumbrances and liens thereon.SourceLaws 1903, c. 73, § 17, p. 391;R.S.1913, § 6305;Laws 1921, c. 133, art. II, § 6, p. 547;C.S.1922, § 5825;C.S.1929, § 77-206;R.S.1943, § 77
